==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Taurid
<hw>Tau"rid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Taurus</ets> +
1st <ets>-id</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Astron.)</fld> <def>Any of a group of
meteors appearing November 20-23; -- so called because they appear to
radiate from a point in Taurus.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

